The paper deals with the computational complexity of the Metric Dimension problem, which is a graph theory problem. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), and Graph Theory (cs.GT) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
